        },
        {
            "title": "美國7月零售銷售普遍攀升 前月數據有所上修",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 受汽車銷售和大型網絡促銷活動的推動，美國7月份零售銷售全面上漲，表明消費者近幾個月增加了支出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國商務部周五公佈的數據顯示，未經通膨調整的零售銷售環比成長0.5%，6月上修後為成長0.9%。不包括汽車在內，零售銷售攀升了0.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Retail Sales Climb in Broad Advance After Upward Revision</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Chris Middleton、Mark Niquette、Reade Pickert.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B7%E6%9C%88%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E6%99%AE%E9%81%8D%E6%94%80%E5%8D%87-%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%88%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E6%9C%89%E6%89%80%E4%B8%8A%E4%BF%AE-124531677.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-15 21:15:47",
